gRI(){return"IMPORTANT: never perform this technique in water, while driving, while standing, or while operating machinery \u2014 loss of consciousness is possible.\n\nContraindications: pregnancy, epilepsy, cardiovascular disease, high blood pressure, panic disorders, recent surgery, glaucoma. If any of these apply to you, consult a doctor before practising.\n\nStart with 3\u20134 cycles and increase gradually."},
